question: virat kohli
answer: Virat Kohli is an Indian international cricketer, former captain of the Indian national team and one of the world's leading batsmen. He is known for his aggressive batting style, record-breaking run totals in both ODIs and Test cricket, and has been named ICC Player of the Year multiple times. He has also led the Royal Challengers Bangalore franchise in the IPL and is considered one of the most successful captains in Indian cricket history.
